tained in the disk of the galaxy would be non-axisymmetric and would rotate\nwith the bar.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Sep 1996 19:05:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Jan 1997 17:13:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 20 May 1997 17:37:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-30"}
